  "description": "<p><strong>作为一家著名的游戏配件和Blade笔记本公司，雷蛇(Razer)现在还提供模拟环绕声的音频软件。</strong>该软件名叫Razer Surround，目前免费向大家提供；不过该公司希望大家能转而向\"儿童游戏慈善机构\"(Child's Play charity)捐款。过了2014年1月，该软件就会恢复19.99美元的零售价。Razer Surround的目标是为一副10美元的立体声头戴式耳机，提供不太昂贵的音频体验。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dd8d6db/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242642.htm&amp;t=%E5%81%9A%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8Razer+Surround%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%A3%B0%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242642.htm&amp;t=%E5%81%9A%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8Razer+Surround%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%A3%B0%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242642.htm&amp;t=%E5%81%9A%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8Razer+Surround%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%A3%B0%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242642.htm&amp;t=%E5%81%9A%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8Razer+Surround%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%A3%B0%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242642.htm&amp;t=%E5